[0]Stephen Samuel writes "The CBC is reporting that Star Trek actor James
Doohan ("Scotty") achieved his hopes of having his ashes launched into
space when a package containing some of his ashes, ashes of Mercury
astronaut Zombie Cooper and about 200 other people were [1]carried into
